UID:99d83366-cf0d-4f3a-9e10-43a03c9e7306
DTSTART:20260718T100000
DTEND:20260718T113000
SUMMARY:RACE: Battersea Park Half Marathon
DESCRIPTION:Target: Sub-1:20 (3:47/km)\nStart: 10:30\nVenue: Carriage Dr E\, London SW11 4NJ\n\nHR strategy:\nkm 0-3: HR 135-138 (settle)\nkm 3-8: HR 138-141 (build)\nkm 8-18: HR 141-145 (race)\nkm 18-21: HR 145-150 (hold)\nFinal km: empty the tank\n\nFuel: vest with electrolytes + chews every 5km.\nDrink at every water station.
END:VEVENT
